1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,150 --> 00:01:40,979
[Go East]

3
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,720
[Episode 7]

4
00:01:44,030 --> 00:01:46,630
Even if you don't transfer to Sifang Pavilion,

5
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,380
don't you have to come here

6
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,000
for foreign-related cases?

7
00:01:50,470 --> 00:01:51,020
Yes!

8
00:01:51,509 --> 00:01:51,990
But...

9
00:01:51,990 --> 00:01:53,110
B-But recently,

10
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:54,759
haven't you been here

11
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:57,370
longer than in Jingzhao?

12
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,520
Isn't that true?

13
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:01,420
That's right.

14
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:04,280
So you are specially in charge of

15
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:07,440
the affairs that connect Jingzhao and Sifang Pavilion.

16
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:09,780
Isn't this also under foreign affairs?

17
00:02:10,380 --> 00:02:11,020
Of course,

18
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:14,260
you're still a military advisor.

19
00:02:14,490 --> 00:02:17,930
You just have one more beautiful badge.

20
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:15,830
[Sifang Pavilion]

21
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:20,810
W-With this badge,

22
00:02:21,670 --> 00:02:23,110
report here every day

23
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:25,390
and save your worries of traveling.

24
00:02:25,579 --> 00:02:26,430
With Wang Kunwu,

25
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:28,390
you'll supervise West Court's affairs.

26
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:30,420
How does that sound?

27
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:33,950
Am I really an equal

28
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,550
of Wang's?

29
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:38,210
Absolutely.

30
00:02:39,150 --> 00:02:39,620
Fine.

31
00:02:40,670 --> 00:02:43,030
But let me make it clear.

32
00:02:43,220 --> 00:02:44,420
If we don't get along,

33
00:02:44,550 --> 00:02:46,370
I'll have to return to Jingzhao.

34
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,920
To you, isn't that...

35
00:02:52,730 --> 00:02:53,400
Hua.

36
00:02:53,610 --> 00:02:55,470
Are you joining Sifang Pavilion?

37
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,090
You should join East Court.

38
00:02:58,270 --> 00:03:00,210
[Huaiyuan Hall]

39
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:01,480
Being with those losers in West Court

40
00:03:01,540 --> 00:03:02,740
will make you stupid.

41
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:09,470
Watch your mouth in the future.

42
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:12,180
The West Court is under my care now.

43
00:03:12,530 --> 00:03:13,260
Understand?

44
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:16,340
No matter how stupid I become, I'd still be smarter than you.

45
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:18,460
Wang Kunwu doesn't dare offend you,

46
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,680
but I'm not afraid.

47
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,510
I threw a fan this time.

48
00:03:24,810 --> 00:03:26,810
Next time, it'll be you whom I throw!

49
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:44,370
She's admired me since we were young.

50
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,400
Why get physical?

51
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:50,350
[West Court]

52
00:03:59,270 --> 00:03:59,710
Move.

53
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:03,750
Why?

54
00:04:04,940 --> 00:04:05,430
[Transfer Order]

55
00:04:06,070 --> 00:04:08,390
On the order of Jingzhao and Ministry of Rites,

56
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:10,790
I've come to supervise at Sifang Pavilion.

57
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,080
This position's mine

58
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:12,890
from now on.

59
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,690
You're in charge of

60
00:04:19,690 --> 00:04:22,550
affairs connecting Jingzhao and Sifang Pavilion,

61
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,560
not everything.

62
00:04:23,590 --> 00:04:24,850
Is there a difference?

63
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,030
Is there a case?

64
00:04:26,030 --> 00:04:26,360
What?

65
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,130
When there's a case,

66
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:31,280
you can exercise your right as a Jingzhao supervisor.

67
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,560
When there's peace,

68
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:34,740
West Court is at my command.

69
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:40,830
Sure.

70
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:44,050
But I can't sit at a subordinate's table.

71
00:04:44,050 --> 00:04:44,710
We'll split

72
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,659
this table in half.

73
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,470
You two,

74
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,610
move the stool here.

75
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:19,610
What are you laughing at?

76
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:21,010
Don't you have work to do?

77
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:22,210
Chen Xiaoshan.

78
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,940
Have you fed Yueying Envoy's chicken?

79
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:25,000
Li Fei, Wang Yubin.

80
00:05:25,150 --> 00:05:26,670
Dongyuan Envoy is moving into a new house.

81
00:05:26,670 --> 00:05:28,130
Don't you need to help him?

82
00:05:29,110 --> 00:05:29,630
You two.

83
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,060
What time is it?

84
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,180
Go stamp the travel passes.

85
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:33,420
-We'll go.
-We'll go.

86
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:35,920
So well trained.

87
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:39,390
Yuan Mo.

88
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:43,480
Go conduct a public inspection of the merchants at West Market.

89
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:47,030
I'm new here. I don't know how to.

90
00:05:55,470 --> 00:05:58,370
When you were selling residence licenses at the city gate,

91
00:05:58,370 --> 00:05:59,830
you didn't seem clueless.

92
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,210
I'm a newbie, right?

93
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:07,520
A business trip on the first day?

94
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,900
You're so ambitious.

95
00:06:09,110 --> 00:06:09,840
I can't do it.

96
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,190
If you disobey your superiors,

97
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,320
you'll be expelled.

98
00:06:13,590 --> 00:06:15,120
That's exactly what I want.

99
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:16,750
What are you doing?

100
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,350
You can't abuse a clerk.

101
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:19,160
We can.

102
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,030
Why?

103
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,280
Yu said so.

104
00:06:21,770 --> 00:06:23,450
Just because Yu said so?

105
00:06:23,550 --> 00:06:23,790
This...

106
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,830
Are you going or not?

107
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:25,090
I...

108
00:06:26,730 --> 00:06:29,570
I'll whip you if you don't go.

109
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:30,560
Are you going...

110
00:06:31,110 --> 00:06:32,350
or not?

111
00:06:34,860 --> 00:06:35,990
I'll go.

112
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,650
Let's start.

113
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,180
Where should we start?

114
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,180
No problem.

115
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:55,950
Wang Kunwu from Sifang Pavilion is here!

116
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,030
I forgot my household registration papers!

117
00:06:58,030 --> 00:06:58,780
Run!

118
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:01,180
I can't afford to offend Wang Kunwu!

119
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:02,670
I'm doomed if he catches me!

120
00:07:02,670 --> 00:07:04,200
The market is closed today.

121
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:05,370
Let's call it a day.

122
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,030
I'm exhausted.

123
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,190
Little Witch.

124
00:07:20,350 --> 00:07:21,410
Get me a jar of wine.

125
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,200
Little Witch!

126
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,230
Hasn't she come back yet?

127
00:07:47,150 --> 00:07:49,810
The medicinal wine she made is quite effective.

128
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:51,710
Much better.

129
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:02,360
Where did this lass go?

130
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:28,180
[Sifang Pavilion]

131
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,080
How dare you ruin my reputation

132
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,650
and disrupt the operation of West Market?

133
00:08:34,650 --> 00:08:35,750
What are you talking about?

134
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:37,030
How dare you deny it?

135
00:08:37,049 --> 00:08:38,250
It was my first business trip.

136
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:39,990
I wanted to use your name to embolden myself.

137
00:08:39,990 --> 00:08:41,070
To think the foreign merchants

138
00:08:41,070 --> 00:08:42,270
would be scared away.

139
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:44,230
Ouch, ouch, ouch.

140
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:47,440
Retainer Wang is lecturing his subordinates again.

141
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,840
You need to lean left.

142
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:50,650
Lean towards the left like this.

143
00:08:50,650 --> 00:08:51,630
It's cooler like this.

144
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,380
Yes, to the left.

145
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:54,040
-To the left?
-Yes, like this.

146
00:08:54,650 --> 00:08:55,580
Yeah? What's up?

147
00:08:56,050 --> 00:08:57,850
We're practicing martial arts.

148
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:58,600
Retainer An.

149
00:08:59,310 --> 00:09:00,170
Care to join us?

150
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:00,810
Come on.

151
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:03,110
Go on.

152
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,270
Childish.

153
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,150
I just didn't want to be embarrassed

154
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:13,550
in front of East Court's people.

155
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:14,700
Then? Go on.

156
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,670
Come on, continue.

157
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,420
Come on. Kill me. Come on.

158
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,150
Let's continue.

159
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,110
Continue what?

160
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:21,840
Cleaning the door?

161
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,150
This door is quite solid.

162
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:23,930
Leave it first.

163
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:25,460
Gather West Court's people

164
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,110
at the retainer's study.

165
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:29,310
I have something important to tell you.

166
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:29,870
Okay.

167
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:32,280
If it weren't for the important announcement,

168
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,480
I'd have retaliated and taken you down.

169
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,440
Mr. Yu, what's this important announcement?

170
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,050
What is it?

171
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,870
My colleagues in West Court,

172
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:46,020
the annual exam for foreign scholars is around the corner.

173
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:47,740
The Central Secretariat has ordered us

174
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:49,090
to cooperate with the Ministry of Personnel

175
00:09:49,090 --> 00:09:51,910
to review the scholars' academic status and qualifications

176
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,310
before approving them for the exam

177
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:56,030
so that the annual exam goes smoothly.

178
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:59,260
Even foreign scholars can take the annual exam?

179
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,300
Good question.

180
00:10:00,830 --> 00:10:04,110
Because Yong is receptive of global talents.

181
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:06,930
Not only can foreign scholars take the exam,

182
00:10:07,090 --> 00:10:10,220
the top-scoring ones can also become officials in Yong.

183
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,930
But the quota is limited.

184
00:10:12,090 --> 00:10:14,090
The competition is fierce.

185
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:15,960
So this matter

186
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:18,950
is the most important job of West Court.

187
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:20,420
West Court's job?

188
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:22,530
What about the East Court?

189
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:24,950
East Court won't take on a time-consuming, laborious,

190
00:10:24,950 --> 00:10:26,270
and profitless job.

191
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:27,550
Mr. Yu.

192
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:29,430
That's unkind of you.

193
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,310
Well...

194
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:36,510
I will personally take charge of West Court

195
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:38,230
and handle the work with you.

196
00:10:38,410 --> 00:10:39,870
Shouldn't you be content?

197
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,660
That's right.

198
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,180
Keep your spirits up.

199
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,660
Keep your spirits up!

200
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,510
Maybe the next Minister of Rites

201
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:54,540
would be one of them.

202
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:57,130
Among these sixth-rates?

203
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,210
What do you mean?

204
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:03,470
Sixth-rates are bottom of the barrel in all six arts.

205
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,790
Long Beina.

206
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,850
He's the son of a rich and powerful man in Yanle.

207
00:11:08,850 --> 00:11:11,180
Right, so what are you complaining about?

208
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:11,910
Stamp it.

209
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:20,530
This is also a sixth-rate.

210
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:21,910
What do these foreign scholars

211
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,120
think of Yong?

212
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:26,450
Retainer Wang.

213
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:29,600
Don't be emotional with your work.

214
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:30,720
Look.

215
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:33,670
He is a royal of Xiyuan.

216
00:11:33,870 --> 00:11:34,800
With this alone,

217
00:11:34,990 --> 00:11:37,520
shouldn't he be approved for the annual exam?

218
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:39,830
Whether he passes or not

219
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:42,360
would depend on his abilities.

220
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:47,260
Go on.

221
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:58,310
Ah Shu, it's time to eat.

222
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,750
Thank you, Ling Xiao.

223
00:12:01,190 --> 00:12:02,230
Don't mention it.

224
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:07,750
I'm sorry about the past.

225
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:09,630
Forget it.

226
00:12:10,070 --> 00:12:12,580
Take it that we got acquainted through fighting.

227
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:13,510
But don't worry.

228
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,710
I'm just staying for a few days.

229
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:16,190
I won't disturb you for too long.

230
00:12:16,190 --> 00:12:17,630
Just stay here in peace.

231
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:18,620
Eat up.

232
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:22,670
I'm so hungry.

233
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,350
Isn't it good?

234
00:12:27,070 --> 00:12:27,710
Yes.

235
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:31,380
Did you quarrel with Young Master Yuan?

236
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:33,790
Don't mention him.

237
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:36,310
What's wrong?

238
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,630
Ling Xiao. Ling Xiao!

239
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:41,670
Young Master Long is here. Come and serve the guest.

240
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:44,070
Ling Xiao.

241
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:45,310
Are you not feeling well?

242
00:12:45,310 --> 00:12:46,650
Every time Young Master Long comes,

243
00:12:46,650 --> 00:12:48,160
I've to serve him no matter what.

244
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:50,280
Young Master Long? Which one?

245
00:12:50,530 --> 00:12:51,820
The son of Yanle's viceroy.

246
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:53,620
You won't know even if I tell you.

247
00:12:58,590 --> 00:12:59,850
-Xiao.
-What’s wrong?

248
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:01,310
Xiao, that man...

249
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:01,670
It's fine.

250
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:03,350
You may leave. I’ll handle it.

251
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:07,260
Young Master Long.

252
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:17,060
Young Master Long.

253
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,680
Why are you unhappy?

254
00:13:21,010 --> 00:13:22,270
Who made you angry?

255
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:31,600
Luckily, not a drop spilled.

256
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,200
Thank you.

257
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,030
Drink up. Drink up.

258
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:53,940
Enjoy the diarrhea later.

259
00:13:57,900 --> 00:13:59,380
Young Master Long!

260
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:00,310
What are you doing?

261
00:14:00,310 --> 00:14:01,300
Young Master Long!

262
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,450
Young Master Long!

263
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,390
Young Master Long.

264
00:14:05,410 --> 00:14:07,050
I'm not feeling well today.

265
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:07,620
Young Master Long!

266
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:09,660
Let's see how unwell you are.

267
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:11,350
No, Young Master Long.

268
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,350
No, Young Master Long!

269
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:13,410
If you obey me,

270
00:14:13,430 --> 00:14:15,230
you could be the viceroy's wife!

271
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,500
Who's that?

272
00:14:25,610 --> 00:14:26,340
Move!

273
00:14:28,010 --> 00:14:31,440
[Ruyi Pavilion]

274
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:38,770
What a wet blanket.

275
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:39,430
Young Master.

276
00:14:39,430 --> 00:14:40,680
Did you see them clearly?

277
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:41,480
A little girl.

278
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:43,400
I've already taught her a lesson.

279
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,330
You are a noble man.

280
00:14:44,330 --> 00:14:45,980
There are many who want to harm you.

281
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:47,510
You need to be more careful.

282
00:14:48,230 --> 00:14:49,430
She's just a thief.

283
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:51,260
I'm not afraid of her!

284
00:14:54,590 --> 00:14:55,390
Young Master.

285
00:14:55,930 --> 00:14:56,810
What's wrong?

286
00:14:59,350 --> 00:15:00,350
What's wrong?

287
00:15:00,350 --> 00:15:01,310
Are you okay?

288
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:02,990
