576
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:09,000
I'm from Sifang Pavilion's West Court.

577
00:30:09,030 --> 00:30:10,190
I'm Wang Kunwu.

578
00:30:26,320 --> 00:30:27,030
I need to pee.

579
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:27,670
Excuse me.

580
00:30:27,670 --> 00:30:27,910
Me too.

581
00:30:27,910 --> 00:30:28,350
Me too.

582
00:30:28,350 --> 00:30:29,010
Stop there!

583
00:30:38,730 --> 00:30:40,530
West Court's Wang Kunwu, right?

584
00:30:41,860 --> 00:30:42,520
They're all here.

585
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:43,180
Still warm.

586
00:30:44,990 --> 00:30:46,720
As members of Sifang Pavilion,

587
00:30:46,970 --> 00:30:48,040
you did such a thing

588
00:30:48,290 --> 00:30:49,370
out of greed.

589
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:50,980
Just like profiteers!

590
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:52,770
If you aren't punished severely,

591
00:30:52,770 --> 00:30:55,500
how could we defend Sifang Pavilion's prestige?

592
00:30:56,490 --> 00:30:57,210
Retainer Wang.

593
00:30:57,210 --> 00:30:57,650
Mr. Yu.

594
00:30:57,680 --> 00:30:58,040
I...

595
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:01,390
Have you forgotten our promise?

596
00:31:02,080 --> 00:31:03,340
Punish them severely.

597
00:31:03,650 --> 00:31:04,930
Absolutely!

598
00:31:05,880 --> 00:31:07,140
You are so ridiculous!

599
00:31:07,910 --> 00:31:08,840
You three will be

600
00:31:09,270 --> 00:31:11,130
fined three months' salary each!

601
00:31:13,170 --> 00:31:17,170
A-And circulate a notice of criticism throughout East and West Courts!

602
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:41,390
What's wrong?

603
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,900
I lost money that I earned.

604
00:31:50,070 --> 00:31:51,130
You've recovered?

605
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:55,100
When I'm so skilled at concocting antidotes, that's a given.

606
00:31:55,100 --> 00:31:55,900
That's right.

607
00:31:56,630 --> 00:31:57,250
By the way,

608
00:31:57,630 --> 00:31:58,890
I also wanted to ask you

609
00:31:58,950 --> 00:32:01,370
why you got attacked by a hidden weapon.

610
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:04,460
A playboy bullied Ling Xiao.

611
00:32:04,870 --> 00:32:07,150
I couldn't stand it, so I got into a fight.

612
00:32:07,470 --> 00:32:08,350
A playboy?

613
00:32:10,500 --> 00:32:11,360
Which playboy?

614
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:12,910
I'll go teach him a lesson!

615
00:32:12,910 --> 00:32:13,600
Forget it.

616
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,390
What will you do with your uncoordinated limbs?

617
00:32:15,390 --> 00:32:16,790
Pay me my monthly salary.

618
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:18,930
I'll let him off for now.

619
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:21,440
What monthly salary?

620
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:23,020
Tomorrow is the first day of the lunar month.

621
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:24,740
I've been cleaning

622
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:25,900
and serving tea.

623
00:32:25,950 --> 00:32:26,850
I won't ask for much.

624
00:32:26,850 --> 00:32:28,050
One string is enough.

625
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:30,410
Settling accounts?

626
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:32,070
Okay. Sure, sure.

627
00:32:32,580 --> 00:32:34,440
Let me calculate things with you.

628
00:32:34,550 --> 00:32:36,340
20 strings for victim compensation.

629
00:32:36,340 --> 00:32:38,020
50 wens for daily breakfast.

630
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:40,400
520 wens for the lounge chair and umbrella.

631
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:42,100
I won't count the emotional distress

632
00:32:42,100 --> 00:32:42,910
from imprisonment.

633
00:32:42,910 --> 00:32:43,910
Including miscellaneous stuff,

634
00:32:43,910 --> 00:32:46,290
you still owe me 21 strings and 272 wens.

635
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:46,920
Pay up.

636
00:32:48,030 --> 00:32:48,960
Yuan Mo.

637
00:32:49,770 --> 00:32:52,540
Is this how you treat a patient who just recovered?

638
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:54,270
You're recovered all the same.

639
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:56,380
Shouldn't we settle the accounts clearly?

640
00:32:56,380 --> 00:32:56,940
Pay up.

641
00:32:57,790 --> 00:32:58,430
Fine!

642
00:32:58,450 --> 00:32:59,820
Let me calculate things with you too.

643
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:01,820
I helped you track down Kudel,

644
00:33:02,250 --> 00:33:02,890
and

645
00:33:03,280 --> 00:33:04,880
I saved your life in Nanshan.

646
00:33:04,910 --> 00:33:05,970
How much are those?

647
00:33:05,990 --> 00:33:08,050
Plus those miscellaneous things...

648
00:33:08,830 --> 00:33:09,430
Yes.

649
00:33:09,670 --> 00:33:10,720
I didn't think it through.

650
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,760
I didn't think it through.

651
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:12,620
How about this?

652
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:13,700
Round it down.

653
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:15,690
You still owe me 21 strings.

654
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:16,210
Pay up.

655
00:33:17,390 --> 00:33:19,470
Is your life just worth 272 wens?

656
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:20,830
Besides,

657
00:33:20,870 --> 00:33:22,590
I'm your maid anyway.

658
00:33:22,610 --> 00:33:24,620
How can we calculate these wages?

659
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:27,970
Stop pushing me to the edge.

660
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,870
Since you violated our agreement

661
00:33:32,870 --> 00:33:34,510
and put me in prison,

662
00:33:35,670 --> 00:33:37,730
we were no longer master and servant.

663
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:40,990
We're just creditor and debtor.

664
00:33:44,430 --> 00:33:45,190
Ouch...

665
00:33:45,750 --> 00:33:46,550
My wound...

666
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:49,340
Sure. Keep acting.

667
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:53,220
You still have to pay me back.

668
00:33:54,930 --> 00:33:57,500
How long will it take to pay this much back?

669
00:33:57,530 --> 00:33:59,940
Don't be anxious. Just pay it back slowly.

670
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:00,800
Look.

671
00:34:01,020 --> 00:34:02,140
Laundry, cooking,

672
00:34:02,300 --> 00:34:04,530
cleaning, and massages all count.

673
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:06,200
I'll pay you at the end of every month.

674
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:08,239
The more work you do, the higher the wage.

675
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:10,400
What if I don't pay you back?

676
00:34:10,679 --> 00:34:13,060
Then even if I've to scratch my entire face,

677
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:15,590
I'll make sure you have a taste of prison life.

678
00:34:39,949 --> 00:34:41,080
Morning, Creditor.

679
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,949
You have a job now.

680
00:34:42,949 --> 00:34:44,949
You need to arrive at Sifang Pavilion on time.

681
00:34:44,949 --> 00:34:47,469
I'm providing you with a wake-up service.

682
00:34:47,790 --> 00:34:49,350
10 wens each. It's cheap.

683
00:34:53,420 --> 00:34:54,350
I can't hear you.

684
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:08,950
50 wens for breakfast.

685
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:12,140
How are a few pancakes worth 50 wens?

686
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:12,870
No problem.

687
00:35:12,890 --> 00:35:15,250
Eat outside if this is too expensive for you.

688
00:35:15,250 --> 00:35:16,650
But I don't know if

689
00:35:17,370 --> 00:35:19,030
you'll make it to work on time.

690
00:35:22,990 --> 00:35:24,140
It's only 50 wens.

691
00:35:24,410 --> 00:35:25,290
I can afford it.

692
00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:27,050
Even so,

693
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:28,510
it'll take at least six or seven years

694
00:35:28,510 --> 00:35:30,240
for you to pay everything back.

695
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,440
Delicious.

696
00:35:35,750 --> 00:35:36,430
10 wens.

697
00:35:37,610 --> 00:35:38,450
20 wens.

698
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:40,350
30 wens.

699
00:35:40,810 --> 00:35:41,360
Hey!

700
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,660
I've... I've already paid.

701
00:35:42,660 --> 00:35:43,510
10 wens to go.

702
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:44,640
50 wens.

703
00:35:51,650 --> 00:35:52,710
What is this again?

704
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,490
My creditor is distinguished.

705
00:35:54,490 --> 00:35:56,370
How can you walk to Sifang Pavilion?

706
00:35:56,370 --> 00:35:58,310
I set up a sedan to pick you up every day.

707
00:35:58,310 --> 00:35:59,760
500 wens back and forth.

708
00:36:00,790 --> 00:36:01,590
I walk faster

709
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:02,870
than them carrying me.

710
00:36:02,890 --> 00:36:03,610
No problem.

711
00:36:03,870 --> 00:36:06,650
The wake-up service can commence an hour earlier.

712
00:36:06,650 --> 00:36:07,530
10 wens extra.

713
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:11,260
I don't need it.

714
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:16,730
Don't follow me. Stop.

715
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:18,750
Don't follow me. It's too high-profile.

716
00:36:18,750 --> 00:36:20,350
Stay away from me. Stay away.

717
00:36:22,530 --> 00:36:23,530
Did you make this?

718
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,560
500 wens per month.

719
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:27,990
If the rouge you make sells well,

720
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,000
I'll pay you more.

721
00:36:29,300 --> 00:36:31,420
So you're willing to hire me?

722
00:36:31,620 --> 00:36:32,880
Come to work tomorrow.

723
00:36:33,230 --> 00:36:34,990
By the way, there's one more thing.

724
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:37,860
Instead of researching my formulas at the shop,

725
00:36:38,190 --> 00:36:39,340
can I do it at home?

726
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,390
I'd like a little more freedom.

727
00:36:40,390 --> 00:36:40,960
Okay.

728
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:44,180
But you have to buy the raw materials yourself.

729
00:36:44,180 --> 00:36:44,870
No problem.

730
00:36:44,910 --> 00:36:46,150
I will work hard.

731
00:36:46,750 --> 00:36:47,680
Thank you, Boss.

732
00:36:47,860 --> 00:36:49,840
[Literature Hall]

733
00:36:49,350 --> 00:36:49,950
Mr. Huang.

734
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:52,110
Every year, when the annual exam is near,

735
00:36:52,110 --> 00:36:54,400
there will always be incompetent scholars from different states

736
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:55,760
scheming to curry favor

737
00:36:55,790 --> 00:36:57,910
for a passing grade to stay in Yong.

738
00:36:58,540 --> 00:37:01,230
This tea shop is their usual hangout spot.

739
00:37:04,370 --> 00:37:06,630
[Mu Yikuan]

740
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:05,790
Yikuan.

741
00:37:05,990 --> 00:37:06,510
Suqin.

742
00:37:07,850 --> 00:37:08,580
Give it to me.

743
00:37:09,270 --> 00:37:09,750
My Lady.

744
00:37:10,430 --> 00:37:11,940
Isn't that Young Master Mu?

745
00:37:11,940 --> 00:37:12,860
Why are you here?

746
00:37:12,730 --> 00:37:14,550
[Bai Suqin]

747
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:13,970
I came to see you.

748
00:37:14,340 --> 00:37:15,230
What do you want to eat later?

749
00:37:15,230 --> 00:37:16,430
My cousin is here too.

750
00:37:16,530 --> 00:37:17,750
I heard Director Bai has agreed

751
00:37:17,750 --> 00:37:20,210
to your cousin's marriage with the lower-status Mu Yikuan.

752
00:37:20,210 --> 00:37:21,620
As long as my cousin is happy,

753
00:37:21,620 --> 00:37:23,250
status doesn't matter.

754
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:26,750
Besides, Mu Yikuan

755
00:37:26,830 --> 00:37:28,870
is much better than those playboys.

756
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:31,390
He's from a poor family but well-educated.

757
00:37:31,390 --> 00:37:33,190
He excels in all the six arts.

758
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:36,490
Director Bai made an exception by accepting him into Literature Hall.

759
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:37,740
Though he's from Yanle,

760
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:39,270
he admires Yong's culture.

761
00:37:39,330 --> 00:37:41,770
He came all the way here to study.

762
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:44,460
He even named himself Mu Yikuan, a Yong name.

763
00:37:45,250 --> 00:37:46,180
Hong Ye and I came

764
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:47,880
to choose fabrics for the wedding outfits,

765
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:49,370
[Maid, Hong Ye]

766
00:37:47,900 --> 00:37:49,500
so I came to see you on the way.

767
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:50,750
Let's go.

768
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:57,190
If only every foreign scholar

769
00:37:57,190 --> 00:37:58,990
could be like Mu Yikuan.

770
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,800
[Sifang Pavilion]

771
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:06,440
Have you heard?

772
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:07,860
When I went to relieve myself,

773
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:09,170
I heard East Court's people saying

774
00:38:09,170 --> 00:38:11,170
that An Xiuyi is meeting Long Beina.

775
00:38:11,940 --> 00:38:12,700
Long Beina?

776
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:14,520
That sixth-rate?

777
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,800
The annual exam is around the corner.

778
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:18,400
If An Xiuyi is meeting him...

779
00:38:19,380 --> 00:38:20,290
Get it?

780
00:38:21,020 --> 00:38:23,550
Is East Court also trying to make a quick buck?

781
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:24,920
It’s possible.

782
00:38:30,410 --> 00:38:31,610
Just do your job well.

783
00:38:32,910 --> 00:38:35,050
Others’ business has nothing to do with West Court.

784
00:38:35,050 --> 00:38:36,060
How does it not?

785
00:38:36,700 --> 00:38:40,030
An Xiuyi's meeting with a foreign scholar before the annual exam.

786
00:38:40,030 --> 00:38:41,640
If it involves money,

787
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:43,710
it's not just East Court

788
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:47,860
but the entire Yong court that will be humiliated!

789
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:50,430
What will the other states

790
00:38:50,580 --> 00:38:52,860
think of Yong then?

791
00:38:54,420 --> 00:38:54,870
Yes...

792
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,140
Where did he go?

793
00:39:06,740 --> 00:39:07,800
Two taels for this.

794
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:10,000
Smell it.

795
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:12,630
Thank you.

796
00:39:15,120 --> 00:39:16,320
Come again next time.

797
00:40:06,650 --> 00:40:08,130
-Why are you here?
-Why are you here?

798
00:40:08,130 --> 00:40:10,370
Retainer Wang, are you following me?

799
00:40:11,650 --> 00:40:13,440
This lady has been following me too.

800
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,200
Wait, you...

801
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,050
Why are you following them?

802
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:17,090
My previous wound

803
00:40:17,090 --> 00:40:18,820
was caused by his subordinate.

804
00:40:21,630 --> 00:40:22,420
Retainer An.

805
00:40:23,150 --> 00:40:23,970
Can you explain

806
00:40:23,970 --> 00:40:25,490
what's in this box?

807
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:26,350
Why should I?

808
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,100
I followed you all the way.

809
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:30,210
You had nothing in your hands.

810
00:40:30,720 --> 00:40:32,150
After you met Young Master Long,

811
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:33,820
this box appeared in your hands.

812
00:40:33,820 --> 00:40:35,140
I have to suspect it.

813
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:36,320
That's right.

814
00:40:36,540 --> 00:40:38,110
I followed him all the way too.

815
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:40,170
This brocade box was originally his.

816
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:41,640
What is this called?

817
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:43,590
Caught red-handed.

818
00:40:44,900 --> 00:40:47,880
You suspect I'm taking bribes from Young Master Long?

819
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,630
If not,

820
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:51,380
why don't you prove your innocence?

821
00:40:51,580 --> 00:40:52,270
Open it.

822
00:40:55,690 --> 00:40:57,350
A row of fine daggers as a gift.

823
00:40:57,350 --> 00:40:58,680
They must be expensive.

824
00:40:59,620 --> 00:41:02,230
In Yanle, these are toys.

825
00:41:03,230 --> 00:41:05,500
I asked Young Master An out to shoot willows in the suburbs.

826
00:41:05,500 --> 00:41:07,620
We used Yong's bows and arrows last time.

827
00:41:07,620 --> 00:41:10,150
This time, we'll use Yanle's flying daggers.

828
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:13,070
So this is called bribery in Yong.

829
00:41:15,690 --> 00:41:16,550
Retainer Wang.

830
00:41:18,030 --> 00:41:20,000
Do you know what willow shooting is?

831
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,380
It doesn't matter if you don't.

832
00:41:21,380 --> 00:41:22,340
If you beg me,

833
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:23,510
I can teach you.

834
00:41:23,890 --> 00:41:25,220
Do I need you to teach me?

835
00:41:26,030 --> 00:41:27,060
So you know how.

836
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:28,680
Do you dare to compete?

837
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:29,160
Sure!

838
00:41:29,180 --> 00:41:30,490
There's a reward.

839
00:41:31,180 --> 00:41:31,840
Wait, wait.

840
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:35,110
Don't act tough.

841
00:41:35,570 --> 00:41:37,120
Willow shooting is a palace game.

842
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:38,970
You can't beat these nobles.

843
00:41:39,190 --> 00:41:40,110
Half a year's salary.

844
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:41,110
Deal.
